name: Nadia X
description: Am honest and faithful also hard working, I am very romantic and I appreciate small things that are done for me. I have a very open and caring heart. I do not like to pretend or to play with someone’s feelings. I am just not capable of doing that. I am cheerful and absolutely happy person. You will be impressed to see how patient, strong but at the same time gentle and sensual I can be. I believe in destiny and I hope to meet my special man here!
